author: Rosie
name: Perform
install_msg:
Thank you for installing this cog!
Do `[p]help CogName` to get the list of commands and their description. If you want to help translate, go to my [crowdin](<https://crowdin.com/project/Star-Cogs>)
If you like my work, [donate me!](<https://ko-fi.com/starcogs>)

There's multiple roleplay-like actions you can perform onto others! Feel free to run `[p]help Perform` to view the commands!
end_user_data_statement: This cog does not persistently store data or metadata about users.
short: Perform Actions like kiss, cuddle etc.
